---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Legal Notice | Théo" lang="en" description="Legal notice and privacy policy for Théo DULUARD's portfolio — GDPR data processing information.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-slate-100">Legal Notice & Personal Data</h1>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-200 mb-4 border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">1. Site publisher</h2>
        <p>This website is published by Théo DULUARD, software engineer (apprenticeship).</p>
        <p>Hosting: GitHub Pages</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-200 mb-4 border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">2. Personal data processing</h2>
        <p>Through the welcome form on this site, personal data (Name and Company) may be collected. Providing this information is strictly <strong>optional</strong> and based on your consent.</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-200 mt-6 mb-2">Purpose of collection</h3>
        <p>This data is collected for purely statistical and professional purposes (audience tracking and recruitment opportunities).</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-200 mt-6 mb-2">Retention period (GDPR)</h3>
        <p>
          In accordance with the storage limitation principle set out in <strong>Article 5.1.e of the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)</strong>, no data is retained beyond the period necessary for its purpose.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Data submitted through the form will be retained for a maximum of <strong>3 years</strong> from the date of collection or our last contact, in line with standard recommendations for professional prospecting.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
          🔗 To learn more about your rights and legal retention periods, you may consult the French data protection authority (CNIL):
          <a href="https://www.cnil.fr/fr/les-durees-de-conservation-des-donnees" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">cnil.fr/les-durees-de-conservation-des-donnees</a>.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-200 mt-6 mb-2">Your rights</h3>
        <p>You have the right to access, rectify, erase, and object to the processing of your personal data. To exercise these rights, please contact me directly via my professional networks (LinkedIn).</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-200 mb-4 border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">3. Automatically collected technical data</h2>
        <p>
          Independently of the welcome form, technical data is automatically collected on each visit on the basis of the <strong>legitimate interest</strong> of the data controller, in accordance with <strong>Article 6.1.f of the GDPR</strong>, for anonymous audience statistics purposes.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-200 mt-6 mb-2">Data collected</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-slate-400">
          <li>Browser and operating system</li>
          <li>Device type (desktop, mobile, tablet)</li>
          <li>Screen resolution and viewport size</li>
          <li>Preferred browser language</li>
          <li>Timezone, country and city of origin (estimated via IP address)</li>
          <li>Page visited and traffic source (referrer)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-200 mt-6 mb-2">Purpose and retention</h3>
        <p>This data is used to understand portfolio audience patterns (devices used, visitor countries, traffic sources) without personal identification. It is retained for <strong>12 months</strong> and is not shared with any third party. No advertising tracking cookies are used.</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-200 mt-6 mb-2">Right to object</h3>
        <p>You may object to this processing at any time by contacting me via LinkedIn. Your request will be handled promptly.</p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
